text: Sukkur City Taluka is an administrative subdivision (taluka) of Sukkur District in the Sindh province of Pakistan. The city of Sukkur is the capital. ==Administration== Sukkur City Taluka is administratively divided into 11 Union Councils.New Sukkur Taluka administratively subdivided into 9 Union Councils.Taluka Municipal Administration Sukkur ==References== Category:Tehsils of Sukkur District
title: Sukkur Taluka
